        <mxCell id="u8TkAXtrdY_UeDioPfuv-30" value="&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Ask the last block number to each peer&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Compute the blocks to ask based on the greatest block number received&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;For each block, compute which peers should have it&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;For each block, ask the peers that should have it to provide the block hash&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Compare the hashes and majority wins&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Continue until the head is reached&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;" style="ellipse;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;aspect=fixed;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="28.75" y="700" width="290" height="290" as="geometry" />
